

---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
import Button from "../components/Button.astro"
---

<Layout>
    <section aria-label="Hero-Section">
        <div class="hero__content">
            <h1>Hi there! I'm <span style='font-family: "Vujahday Script", cursive;'>Jack</span>, and I enjoy transforming ideas into captivating digital experiences.</h1>
            <Button />
        </div>
    </section>

    <section aria-label="About">
        <div class="about">
            <div class="about__img">

            </div>

            <div class="about__content">
                <h2>About Me</h2>

                <p>Hello, and welcome to my portfolio! I'm Jack, a passionate software developer who enjoys crafting digital experiences that leave a lasting impression. As a software developer, I thrive on turning ideas into reality through code. My journey as a software developer has been an exciting one, filled with countles opportunities to learn, grow, and create.</p>

                <p>In my spare time, I enjoy contributing to the open-source community, attending tech meetups, and participating in hackathons. These activities allow me to engage with other talented professionals and broaden my knowledge base.</p>

                <p>I am thrilled by the opportunity to work on challenging projects that have a meaningful impact. If you are looking for a dedicated and versatile software developer who can bring your ideas to life, I would love to connect with you. Let's collaborate and create exceptional software together.</p>

                <p>Thank you for taking the time to visit my portfolio. I look forward to hearing from you!</p>

                <Button title="Go To My Portfolio" />

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>


<style>
    .hero__content {
        display: grid;
        justify-items: center;
        align-content: center;
        gap: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
        padding-block: 8rem;
        color: #fff;
        background: rgb(0 0 0 / .5);
        background-image: url(/assets/nubelson-fernandes-small.jpg);
        background-blend-mode: multiply;
        background-size: cover;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-position-x: -100px;
    }

    h1 {
        width: min(90%, 700px);
        margin: auto;
        font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2vw + .5rem, 2rem);
    }

    .about {
        width: min(90%, 1200px);
        margin: auto;
        padding-block: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .about__content {
        display: grid;
        justify-items: center;
        gap: 2rem;    
    }

    .about__content h2 {
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 2vw + .5rem, 3rem);
        color: var(--clr-accent-3);
    }

    .about__content p {
        font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 1.2vw + .5rem, 2rem);

    }
</style>


